無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔開冷氣零晨真係....嘈死 痕死"},{"pid":"651a8932ed2ce26cb3894aa5ebd1cd57750f8d2f","tid":34082,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為有蚊先開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 斷鳩估我樓上唔會日日有蚊掛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你樓上係咪有養狗？<br />\n好多人對狗好過對人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話唔定係俾狗嘆冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2faaffcd6bb5a1dfebce31f03e96ca9bdc9106b","tid":34082,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屍體冇咁快腐爛 樓主小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽講話有蛆蟲係天花板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfc6a2c414eed86a4f0b221c98ece454bb59a48","tid":34082,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:33:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為收藏野要保持特定温度同濕度都會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcac77a95a1bcb2efb79e9461934414eb513102","tid":34082,"uid":15639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T09:33:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我有朋友因爲屋企單位係特色天台户<br />\n天台冇種植物<br />\n所以一年四季都開冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講多少少得唔得  無咩文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n姐係佢唔開冷氣 吸普通空氣 好污濁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n特色天台户係複式單位<br />\n好多人會整得好靚，好時尚，當係一個私人空間<br />\n未必會種植物，會有蚊蟲<br />\n咁頂層就會有陽光長期曬住<br />\n天花板咪會受熱<br />\n就算樓下單位有對流窗一樣會好熱<br />\n所以我朋友係一年四季長開冷氣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\